<template>
     <JqxButton @click="onClickSave" :template="'success'" :width="80" 
     style="float: left; margin-left: 4px; margin-top: 10px">
     Success</JqxButton>
</template>

<script>
import JqxButton from 'jqwidgets-scripts/jqwidgets-vue/vue_jqxbuttons.vue';
export default {
  data() {
    return {
        kpiDataItem: ''
    }
  },
  methods: {
    async onClickSave() {
      await fetch('http://localhost:5000/api/kpvitem', {
        method: 'POST',
        data: this.kpiDataItem
      })

      this.kpiDataItem = ''
    }
  }
}
</script>
